          "_name": "article08",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article8\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Content Width\" name=\"contentWidth\" min=\"8\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Wrap Bg\" name=\"wrapBgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"card col-md-12 col-lg-{{contentWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"card-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"image-wrapper d-flex justify-content-center mb-4\">\n            <img mbr-if=\"showImage\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/stressed1-1408x670.png\" alt=\"Stressed Man\">\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"card-content-text\">\n            <h3 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style mbr-white mt-3 mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .card-box\"><b>Common Line Ware Issues With</b><br><b>Quick Fixes</b></h3>\n          <div class=\"row card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 active\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>Welcome!</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">In today's fast paced world, we don't have time for things to go wrong. But occasionally they do. In this post we're looking at some common issues and their simple fixes to get you back up and running in no time.<br><br><br></p>\n              </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>My website is live but I'm not receiving emails</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">This is a common issue in the first hour after your website goes live. Email settings take a little time to apply across the internet — this is completely normal.\n<br>Here's what to do:\n<br>\n<br>Wait up to one hour after your website goes live for all email settings to apply fully.\n<br>Check your inbox for a forwarding confirmation email from Cloudflare or Google. You must accept this to activate email forwarding to your address.\n<br>Send yourself a test email to your new address and check it arrives in your inbox.\n<br>\n<br>If you've followed all of these steps and emails are still not arriving, feel free to contact our friendly support team using the link below.<br><br><br></p>\n              </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>I've set up my LW Plus Addon phone app but I can't receive calls</b></h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">I've set up my phone app but I can't receive calls<br>If you've scanned your QR code and can make outbound calls but incoming calls aren't coming through, the issue is usually your availability status in the app.<br>Here's what to do:<br><br>Open your 3CX app and look at the top right corner.<br>Find the person icon with a headset. If it is grey, tap it to turn it blue. This activates call receiving.<br>Check the small square next to the person icon. If it is any colour other than green, tap it and select Available.<br>Your person icon should now be blue and your status green. You should now be able to receive calls.<br>If calls are still not coming through, check your internet connection, a weak connection can prevent incoming calls.<br><br>If you're still experiencing issues after following these steps, our support team is here to help. Visit the link below to get in touch.</p>\n              </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n              <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">My website is live but I'm not receiving emails</h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">This is a common issue in the first hour after your website goes live. Email settings take a little time to apply across the internet, this is completely normal.<br>Here's what to do:<br><br>Wait up to one hour after your website goes live for all email settings to apply fully.<br>Check your inbox for a forwarding confirmation email from Cloudflare or Google. You must accept this to activate email forwarding to your address.<br>Send yourself a test email to your new address and check it arrives in your inbox.<br><br>If you've followed all of these steps and emails are still not arriving, feel free to contact our friendly support team using the link below.<br><br>Still Need Help? <a href=\"index.html#contacts01-i\" class=\"text-warning\">Click Here</a><br>Call Us: <a href=\"tel:+443305202132\" class=\"text-warning\">0330 520 2132</a><br><br>We're here to help at every step.<br><br></p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            \n\n            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-warning-outline\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" href=\"what-line-ware-can-do-for-trade.html\">Previous Post:&nbsp;7 Line Ware</a> <a class=\"btn btn-warning\" href=\"dedicated-numbers-for-business.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Next Post: 2 Business Phone</a></div>\n          </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vdHDmDztS8",
          "_anchor": "article08-t",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
